    "<p>First Professor of Fine Arts, Harvard University; influential mentor for a generation of art historians.": [],
    "Norton was born to a wealthy Boston family with strong intellectual interests.": [],
    "His father, Andrews Norton (1786-1853), was a Unitarian theologian and professor of sacred literature at Harvard.": [],
    "The younger Norton\u00a0attended Harvard University, graduating with an A. B. in 1846.": [],
