    "With his various attempts at business a failure, he returned to Europe in 1855, remaining there until 1857.": [],
    "In Switzerland, Norton met <a href=\"/ruskinj\">John Ruskin</a>,\u00a0\u00a0the art critic and historian whose writings deeply affected him.": [],
    "Norton returned to focus on writing and literature.": [],
    "He edited the <em>North American Review</em> between 1864-68 and co-founded <em>The Nation</em> in 1865.": [],
    "His articles at this time demonstrated both a knowledge in art history and archaeology as well as literature.": [
